---
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";

interface Props {
  dyspan2025Src: string;
  wioptReceptionSrc: string;
  icc2024Src: string;
  iccCcSrc: string;
  dyspanAward1Src: string;
  dyspanAward2Src: string;
}

const {
  dyspan2025Src,
  wioptReceptionSrc,
  icc2024Src,
  iccCcSrc,
  dyspanAward1Src,
  dyspanAward2Src,
} = Astro.props;
---

<section class="section" id="news">
  <SectionTitle title="News" />
  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-date">May 2025</div>
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-card">
        <h3>Presented Our Paper at IEEE DySPAN2025.</h3>
        <p>I had the privilege of presenting our paper “Compete or Coordinate? Analysis of Spectrum Sharing Strategies for Local Wireless Services”. 

          Huge thanks to my incredible co-authors for their collaboration and guidance throughout this project Zongyun Xie Igor Kadota Randall Berry Carlos Caicedo William Lehr!</p>
        <img
          class="timeline-image"
          src={dyspan2025Src}
          alt="DySPAN 2025 presentation"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-date">Oct 2024</div>
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-card">
        <h3>Received Best Student Paper Award at IEEE WiOPT2024!</h3>
        <p>Thrilled to share that our paper, "Impact of Geographical Separation on Spectrum Sharing Markets," co-authored with Zongyun Xie, Igor Kadota, Randall A Berry has received the Best Student Paper Award at the IEEE 22nd International Symposium on Modeling and Optimization in Mobile, Ad hoc, and Wireless Networks (WiOPT) 2024!</p>
        <img
          class="timeline-image"
          src={wioptReceptionSrc}
          alt="WiOpt 2024 reception"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-date">Jun 2024</div>
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-card">
        <h3>Presented Our Paper at IEEE ICC2024.</h3>
        <p>Had a great time at IEEE ICC 2024 presenting our work "Market Impacts of Relaxed Incumbent Protection in Spectrum Sharing," co-authored with Prof. Randall Berry. Great to meet our alumnus Dr. Cheng Chen, now a Wireless Standards Engineer at Intel!</p>
        <div class="timeline-images">
          <img
            class="timeline-image"
            src={icc2024Src}
            alt="ICC 2024"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <img
            class="timeline-image"
            src={iccCcSrc}
            alt="IEEE ICC 2024 conference photo"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-date">May 2024</div>
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-card">
        <h3>Received Best Paper Award (Policy Track) at IEEE DySPAN2024!</h3>
        <p>Thrilled to share that our paper, "Market Impacts of Pooling Intermittent Spectrum," co-authored with Prof. Randall Berry has received the Best Paper Award (policy track) at the IEEE International Symposium on Dynamic Spectrum Access Networks (DySPAN) 2024!</p>
        <div class="timeline-images">
          <img
            class="timeline-image"
            src={dyspanAward1Src}
            alt="Dyspan 2024 Award Photo 1"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <img
            class="timeline-image"
            src={dyspanAward2Src}
            alt="Dyspan 2024 Award Photo 2"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-date">Nov 2023</div>
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-card">
        <h3>Passed PhD Qualifying Exam.</h3>
        <p>This is the first milestone of my PhD journey!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
